I never root. It just annoys me to no end, mobs seem to break out of it far too often. Yes sometimes I will do what you do - let my shaman tank one (yes I also concentrate on HP/AC gear for my shammy, though I've been kind of cheap with her stuff) while I kill another real fast. It works quite well if I do it every so often but don't think I could handle every single pull being two without there being some downtime (especially if they're not the lowest dark blue you could possibly find). <br>
